title: Go Get My Lunch 2020
itunes:title: Go Get My Lunch 2020
description:
A room filled with hereos - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal bring you all of the latest news around the NFL. Clowney goes to the Titans, Trubisky is named the Bears starter and Deshaun Watson signs a monster deal. We talk some other big contracts and where Adrian Peterson lands before giving our sandwich props for the 2020 season.
